    "output": "```python\ndef fibonacci(n):\n    if n <= 0:\n        return []\n    elif n == 1:\n        return [0]\n    \n    sequence = [0, 1]\n    while len(sequence) < n:\n        sequence.append(sequence[-1] + sequence[-2])\n        \n    return sequence\n```",
